-- Chesapeake Considering Sale of All Permian Basin Assets
-- B y   T i n a   D a v i s
-- 2012-02-13T13:02:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-13/chesapeake-considering-sale-of-all-permian-basin-assets.html
Chesapeake Energy Corp. (CHK)  will
consider a sale of its Permian Basin assets, which represent 5
percent of total production, “if it receives a compelling
offer.”  The company issued a statement on its 2012 financial plan
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tina Davis at 
 tinadavis@bloomberg.net  